Joanne Dru https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joanne_Dru 0 Joanne Dru (born Joan Letitia LaCock, January 31, 1922 – September 10, 1996) was an American film and television actress, known for such films as Red River, She Wore a Yellow Ribbon, and All the King's Men.
